      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PSIONIC PROWESS (1) jumps from box 1 for the first time after placing latest at Capalaba (20.09) in a Grade 6. Overdue and gets her chance. LAKODA JILL (7) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with her maiden win, then finished a 6 length second last start at this track over 352m (20.09). Has placed 10 times at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. ORIGINALITY (8) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a PM winner three back (22.65) at this track over 390m. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. GOLDSTAR FOSTER (6) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
